edin of Iran]] |Killed along with 72 others in the [[Hafte Tir bombing]] |- |rowspan=2|August 30, 1981 |[[Mohammad Ali Rajai]], president of Iran |rowspan=2|[[Massoud Keshmiri]], an operative of the [[People's Mujahedin of Iran]] | |- |[[Mohammad Javad Bahonar]], Prime Minister of Iran | |- |January 11, 2012 |[[Mostafa Ahmadi-Roshan]], nuclear scientist and university professor | |Killed by a bomber from a motorcycle |}
